data.description: Freshly updated ranch on close to an acre! Home sits on large corner lot and has 4 spacious bedrooms with 2 full bathrooms and large, open living spaces.  Interior has all new paint. Newly refinished hardwood floors throughout entry, living room and eat in kitchen.  Bedrooms have all new carpet. Kitchen boasts vaulted ceilings with lots of kitchen cabinets, all newly painted and granite countertops. New lighting and fixtures throughout home. HVAC and water tank new this year and roof and well only 5 years old. Attached, oversized 1 car garage is great for parking and storage. Property also has attached additional storage area and a storm shelter in the backyard.
